### ðŸ¦„ Run Unitxt Exploration Dashboard

To launch unitxt graphical user interface run:
```
unitxt-explore
```

# ðŸ¦„ Contributors

Please install Unitxt from source by:
```
git clone git@github.com:IBM/unitxt.git
cd unitxt
pip install -e ".[dev]"
pre-commit install
```

